<p class="eyebrow" style="margin-top:1.4rem">Press / Media kit</p>
<h1 class="t">Press kit</h1>
<p class="dek">Everything you need to write about Hypercreative: logos, the brand manual, colours, type and boilerplate. If you need anything else, just ask.</p>

<h2>Boilerplate</h2>
<span class="lead">Short</span>
<div class="bp-card"><button class="copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy short boilerplate">Copy</button><p>Hypercreative trains the teams of the world&#8217;s most demanding companies to create useful ideas on demand. It turns creativity from a personality trait into a trainable discipline.</p></div>
<span class="lead">Long</span>
<div class="bp-card"><button class="copy" type="button" aria-label="Copy long boilerplate">Copy</button><p>Hypercreative is a corporate creativity training company. It teaches leadership teams and their people to generate useful, original ideas on demand, through keynotes and tailor-made programmes. The method was built inside high-pressure creative teams in film and production and is now exported to large organisations. Hypercreative is a trademark.</p></div>

<h2>Logo</h2>
<p>Always use the supplied files. Keep clear space around the wordmark and never alter, recolour, rotate or re-typeset it. See the brand manual for full rules.</p>
<div class="logo-grid">
<div><div class="logo-card light"><img src="../assets/press/logo-light.svg" alt="Hypercreative wordmark in dark on a light background"></div><div class="dls"><a class="dl" href="../assets/press/logo-light.svg" download><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3v12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l4-4M5 21h14"/></svg> SVG</a><a class="dl" href="../assets/press/logo-light.png" download><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3v12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l4-4M5 21h14"/></svg> PNG</a></div></div>
<div><div class="logo-card dark"><img src="../assets/press/logo-dark.svg" alt="Hypercreative wordmark reversed in light on a dark background"></div><div class="dls"><a class="dl" href="../assets/press/logo-dark.svg" download><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3v12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l4-4M5 21h14"/></svg> SVG</a><a class="dl" href="../assets/press/logo-dark.png" download><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3v12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l4-4M5 21h14"/></svg> PNG</a></div></div>
